THE Lephalale Regional Court has sentenced two rhino
poachers to 15-years imprisonment on Wednesday.   The duo, Sam Mnone (35) and Mtheto Kenny Sibiya (34) were
sentenced to for the unlawful possession of a firearm, unlawful possession of
ammunition, illegal hunting of protected animals and trespassing.The court heard that at Zonderwater Rhinoland game rangers in
